1. Installation
Device A: "pip install fastapi uvicorn pydantic speechrecognition pyttsx3 paho-mqtt 
deep-translator requests"
Device B: "pip install paho-mqtt gTTS"

2. On device A, open the terminal and enter "uvicorn local_api:app --port 7071"

3. On device B, run "python codedeviceB.py"

4. On device A, run "python codedeviceA.py"

